    <releaseNotes>
- Updated DiskObserver folder size monitoring to ignore unauthorized folder/file access issues during file size summation. This does not involve exception handling.
- DiskObserver Folder Size monitoring now supports Environment variables in fullpath/thresholdMB pair setting (e.g., %SOMEFULLPATHENVVAR%, 1000 | %SOMEPATH%\SomeFolder, 2000).
- Updated error codes to match new DiskObserver feature.
- Updated KVS LVID perf counter impl.
- Removed concurrent processing support in FabricSystemObserver.
- Updated OSObserver InfraStructureService deployment check impl.
- Performance improvements across memory and CPU usage.
- Extensibility dll version now matches FabricObserver's.
- Added work around (auto-mitigation) to SF Cluster Upgrades unsetting Caps on FO's Linux Caps binaries.
	</releaseNotes>
